name: MS.YOU
description:
We're no more than mere radio waves wandering in black space, repeatedly shaping our form and way in forms and ways that may suddenly, accidentally, unexpectedly fit each other.

In celebrating of hicetnunc project's 6 months on September 2021.
Monochrome edition minted in 26 copies. 3000x3000 px.
Original piece is a digital vector artwork, handmade in 2010.
